<note n="0353002" resp="#resp1" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0353002">尊【大】，〔－〕【宋】</note>
<note n="0353003" resp="#resp1" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0353003">大唐京兆【大】，唐朝散朗【宋】【元】【明】</note>
